world’s trade and controlling one of the world’s largest countries.

00:00:43.969 --> 00:00:49.419
So, let’s get right into the cut-throat capitalist story of The East India Company

00:00:51.329 --> 00:00:55.319
Our story starts back in 1600, in London.

00:00:56.409 --> 00:01:00.297
Although a couple of hundred years later, by the 1800s.

